<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Support Us — The Political Rant</title>
<meta name="description" content="Support The Political Rant — India's unfiltered, cross-spectrum political news aggregator. No ads, no algorithm, just honest curation.">

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo+Black&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  :root{
    --paper:#121212;
    --ink:#ECE9E2;
    --ink-dim:#8c8a85;
    --rule:#34322e;
    --red:#e8401f;
    --display: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
    --body: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    --mono: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }

  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}
  body{
    background:var(--paper);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-family:var(--body);
    line-height:1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  a{color:inherit; text-decoration:none;}

  body::before{
    content:"";
    position:fixed; inset:0;
    pointer-events:none;
    background-image:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size:3px 3px;
    z-index:1;
  }

  .wrap{max-width:680px; margin:0 auto; position:relative; z-index:2;}

  header.masthead{
    padding:28px 20px 22px;
    border-bottom:3px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .eyebrow-row{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:0.08em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--ink-dim);
    margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  .eyebrow-row .dot{color:var(--red);}

  h1.title{
    font-family:var(--display);
    font-size:clamp(32px, 9vw, 46px);
    line-height:0.95;
    text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  h1.title .rant{color:var(--red);}

  .nav-row{
    display:flex; gap:16px; margin-top:16px;
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11.5px;
    letter-spacing:0.04em; text-transform:uppercase;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .nav-row a{
    color:var(--ink-dim);
    border-bottom:1px solid transparent;
    padding-bottom:2px;
    transition:all 0.15s ease;
  }
  .nav-row a:hover, .nav-row a.active{
    color:var(--ink);
    border-bottom-color:var(--red);
  }

  main{padding:36px 20px 80px;}

  .intro-eyebrow{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:0.1em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--red);
    margin-bottom:10px;
  }

  h2.section-title{
    font-family:var(--display);
    font-size:clamp(26px, 7vw, 36px);
    line-height:1.1;
    margin-bottom:18px;
  }

  p{
    font-size:15px;
    color:var(--ink-dim);
    margin-bottom:14px;
    max-width:58ch;
  }
  p strong{color:var(--ink); font-weight:600;}

  /* ---------- COST BREAKDOWN ---------- */
  .breakdown{
    border-top:1px solid var(--rule);
    padding-top:28px;
    margin-top:8px;
    margin-bottom:36px;
  }
  .breakdown-title{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:0.08em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--ink-dim);
    margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .breakdown-row{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:baseline;
    padding:12px 0;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule);
    gap:20px;
  }
  .breakdown-item{font-size:14.5px; color:var(--ink);}
  .breakdown-cost{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:13px;
    color:var(--ink-dim);
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .breakdown-total{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:baseline;
    padding:14px 0 0;
    gap:20px;
  }
  .breakdown-total .breakdown-item{
    font-family:var(--display);
    font-size:16px;
  }
  .breakdown-total .breakdown-cost{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:14px;
    color:var(--ink);
    font-weight:600;
  }

  /* ---------- UPI SECTION ---------- */
  .upi-section{
    border:1px solid var(--red);
    padding:28px 24px;
    margin-bottom:28px;
  }

  .upi-label{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:10.5px;
    letter-spacing:0.08em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--red);
    margin-bottom:8px;
  }

  .upi-title{
    font-family:var(--display);
    font-size:24px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
  }

  .upi-desc{
    font-size:14px;
    color:var(--ink-dim);
    margin-bottom:24px;
    max-width:52ch;
  }

  /* QR + ID side by side on desktop, stacked on mobile */
  .upi-body{
    display:flex;
    gap:28px;
    align-items:flex-start;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
  }

  /* ---------- QR CODE ---------- */
  .qr-wrap{
    flex:0 0 auto;
    width:180px;
    height:180px;
    border:1px solid var(--rule);
    background:#1e1e1e;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .qr-wrap img{
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    object-fit:contain;
    display:block;
  }
  .qr-placeholder{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:10px;
    color:var(--ink-dim);
    text-align:center;
    line-height:1.6;
    padding:16px;
    letter-spacing:0.04em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
  }

  /* ---------- UPI ID + COPY ---------- */
  .upi-right{
    flex:1;
    min-width:200px;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:14px;
    justify-content:center;
  }

  .upi-box{
    background:#1e1e1e;
    border:1px solid var(--rule);
    padding:16px 18px;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;
    gap:12px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .upi-id{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:15px;
    font-weight:600;
    color:var(--ink);
    letter-spacing:0.03em;
  }
  .upi-copy{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:0.06em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--ink);
    background:transparent;
    border:1px solid var(--rule);
    padding:8px 14px;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:all 0.15s ease;
    flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .upi-copy:hover{
    background:var(--ink);
    color:var(--paper);
    border-color:var(--ink);
  }

  .upi-steps{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:11px;
    color:var(--ink-dim);
    line-height:2;
    letter-spacing:0.02em;
  }
  .upi-steps span{
    color:var(--ink);
    font-weight:600;
  }

  /* ---------- CALLOUT ---------- */
  .callout{
    border-left:3px solid var(--red);
    padding:14px 18px;
    margin:0 0 28px;
    background:rgba(232,64,31,0.06);
  }
  .callout p{margin-bottom:0; font-size:14px;}

  footer{
    padding:30px 20px 50px;
    border-top:1px solid var(--rule);
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:11px;
    color:var(--ink-dim);
    line-height:1.7;
  }
  footer a{color:var(--ink); border-bottom:1px solid var(--red);}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="wrap">

  <header class="masthead">
    <div class="eyebrow-row"><span class="dot">●</span> SUPPORT THE PROJECT</div>
    <h1 class="title">THE POLITICAL<br><span class="rant">RANT</span></h1>
    <nav class="nav-row">
      <a href="index.html">Feed</a>
      <a href="politics101.html">Politics 101</a>
      <a href="about.html">About Us</a>
      <a href="support.html" class="active">Support Us</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>

    <div class="intro-eyebrow">Keep the lights on</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">No ads. No algorithm.<br>Just you.</h2>
    <p>The Political Rant runs on zero budget and zero advertising. Every story is picked by hand, every source is credited, and no one is paying to get their coverage here. If you find this useful, a small contribution goes directly toward keeping the site alive.</p>
    <p><strong>Here's exactly what it costs to run this site:</strong></p>

    <div class="breakdown">
      <div class="breakdown-title">Annual running costs</div>
      <div class="breakdown-row">
        <span class="breakdown-item">Domain name (.in or .com)</span>
        <span class="breakdown-cost">Rs 700 – 1,000 / year</span>
      </div>
      <div class="breakdown-row">
        <span class="breakdown-item">Hosting (GitHub Pages)</span>
        <span class="breakdown-cost">Free</span>
      </div>
      <div class="breakdown-row">
        <span class="breakdown-item">Time spent curating stories</span>
        <span class="breakdown-cost">Unpaid</span>
      </div>
      <div class="breakdown-total">
        <span class="breakdown-item">Total hard cost</span>
        <span class="breakdown-cost">~Rs 1,000 / year</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- UPI SECTION -->
    <div class="upi-section">
      <div class="upi-label">Pay via UPI</div>
      <div class="upi-title">Scan or copy the ID</div>
      <div class="upi-desc">Works with any UPI app — GPay, PhonePe, Paytm, BHIM. Any amount welcome, even Rs 10.</div>

      <div class="upi-body">

        <!-- QR CODE -->
        <!-- TO ADD YOUR QR: upload your QR image to GitHub repo, rename it "upi-qr.png", done -->
        <div class="qr-wrap">
          <img src="upi-qr.png" alt="UPI QR code"
            onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';">
          <div class="qr-placeholder" style="display:none;">Upload<br>upi-qr.png<br>to repo</div>
        </div>

        <div class="upi-right">
          <div class="upi-box">
            <!-- REPLACE yourname@upi WITH YOUR ACTUAL UPI ID -->
            <span class="upi-id" id="upi-id">9392615805@fam</span>
            <button class="upi-copy" onclick="copyUPI()">Copy ID</button>
          </div>
          <div class="upi-steps">
            <span>Step 1</span> — Open any UPI app<br>
            <span>Step 2</span> — Scan the QR or send to ID<br>
            <span>Step 3</span> — Enter any amount
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="callout">
      <p>Even Rs 50 from 20 readers covers the domain for a year. Not in a position to contribute? Sharing the site with one person who'd find it useful is genuinely just as valuable.</p>
    </div>

  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>All contributions go directly toward running costs. This site has no company behind it, no investors, and no advertising revenue.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:10px;"><a href="index.html">← Back to the feed</a></p>
  </footer>

</div>

<script>
  function copyUPI(){
    const id = document.getElementById('upi-id').textContent;
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(id).then(() => {
      const btn = document.querySelector('.upi-copy');
      btn.textContent = 'Copied!';
      setTimeout(() => btn.textContent = 'Copy ID', 2000);
    });
  }
</script>

</body>
</html>
